column2: "Thank you for getting all of us the things we were looking for."
"I was just thinking, we're all in swimsuits right now. Why don't we go to the sea and make some memories there?"
"Sounds good! Let's get out there and start enjoying summer!"

"Hehe...
Certainly, that sounds like it will be fun. I have no objections."

"We'll need your help, <%me>.
Please take us down to the sea!"
